repository.name: microservices-core
repository.description: This repo uses three simple services to illustrate how most distributed microservice architecture systems work. We use Go for creating a reverse proxy and Java for service discovery and registering profiles.  The services use heartbeats to stay registered. We use the MySQL database in service registry and profile.
